title: 10 year
body: It is the end of the 10 year anniversary, and i didn't get anything. I looked through my skins and didn't get nothing. What a nice thing that i get for being with league for over 8 years... Great

replies.body: It's not the end! We've been sending out the gifts in waves to ensure they get out properly. If you don't have anything by the 23rd, please let me know.
